items.raw_string: From 1 January 2017 until further notice, adviser to Brand Communications, 28-29 Threadneedle Street, London EC2R 8AY, a company which exists to build iconic brands for Africa. I consulted ACoBA about this appointment. (Registered 17 January 2017)
